<plot>The horse cart driver takes his kids to the school. But that day children decide not to go the school. Instead they start wandering around the island and collect all items they can find on the streets from disposed tire to card board boxes. Then they go to the church hill and collect all colorful fabrics put on trees as symbols of the wishes made by women. Finally, they go to their 'toy factory' to build the wishes as toys for children.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?419224</url></doc>
